de: Amendment to the Loan Agreement concluded on December 5th, 1980, between the Federal Office for External Economic Affairs (FOEEA) and the Industrial Development Bank Limited (IDB) on the granting of a mixed credit and to the Guarantee Agreement between the Republic of Kenya and the Swiss Confederation, dated December 11th, 1981 (Texte original envoyé aux AF le 7.6.1994) - 13-05-1994 - Bürgschaftsabkommen zwischen der Schweizerischen Eidgenossenschaft und der Republik Kenia
